The code has worked best for:
1) Python 2.7, 32 Bit
2) VLC 2.08, 32 Bit
3) Required library installation: 
•	python-vlc
o	installation command: python  -m pip install python-vlc
•	PILLOW
o	installation command: python  -m pip install PILLOW
•	Numpy
o	installation command: python  -m pip install  numpy
•	Pathlib
o	installation command: python  -m pip install  pathlib
